Colledge counselor collaborative management SaaS service

Counselor AssistanT is a SaaS-based collaborative management service for colledge counselors, which can assist colledge counselors and their student teams rapidly improve daily student management efficiency and establish a collaborative network for ideological and political education. Achieve precise education and nurturing through data-driven approaches.
source: 江苏金智教育信息股份有限公司
